13
00:00:38.170 --> 00:00:42.320
I've always wondered you, day and night.

14
00:00:42.320 --> 00:00:44.509
Isn't that enough?

15
00:00:44.509 --> 00:00:45.509
You're not believing.

16
00:00:45.509 --> 00:00:48.509
Sorry I wasn't brave enough to tell you the truth.

17
00:00:48.509 --> 00:00:50.979
I don't know.

18
00:00:50.979 --> 00:00:51.979
Don't be mad.

19
00:00:51.979 --> 00:00:52.979
Why are you leaving?

